<div class="docs-section">
  <h2 class="docs-section__title">Default Tabs</h2>
  <p class="docs-section__description">Use to divide related content into parallel sections a user navigates between without leaving the page — course overview, modules, and entry requirements are a common pattern. Best for 2–5 tabs; if more sections are needed, consider a side navigation instead. The underline active indicator keeps the UI lightweight and editorial.</p>
  <div class="ds-preview">
    <div class="ds-preview__content" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch;">
      <div class="tabs">
        <div class="tabs__list" role="tablist">
          <button class="tabs__trigger tabs__trigger--active" role="tab" aria-selected="true">Overview</button>
          <button class="tabs__trigger" role="tab" aria-selected="false">Modules</button>
          <button class="tabs__trigger" role="tab" aria-selected="false">Entry Requirements</button>
          <button class="tabs__trigger" role="tab" aria-selected="false" disabled>Disabled</button>
        </div>
        <div class="tabs__panel" role="tabpanel">
          <p class="text-body">This course provides a comprehensive foundation in business management principles.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tabs__panel" role="tabpanel" hidden>
          <p class="text-body">Year 1: Introduction to Business, Marketing Fundamentals, Economics.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tabs__panel" role="tabpanel" hidden>
          <p class="text-body">UCAS points: 112-128. IELTS: 6.0 overall.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="docs-section">
  <h2 class="docs-section__title">Pill Tabs</h2>
  <p class="docs-section__description">Use as a filter or toggle control rather than a content organiser — switching between undergraduate, postgraduate, and short courses in a listing view, for example. The contained pill shape gives a stronger interactive affordance and suits compact or card-embedded contexts where the default underline tab would feel too editorial.</p>
  <div class="ds-preview">
    <div class="ds-preview__content" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch;">
      <div class="tabs tabs--pills">
        <div class="tabs__list" role="tablist">
          <button class="tabs__trigger tabs__trigger--active" role="tab" aria-selected="true">Undergraduate</button>
          <button class="tabs__trigger" role="tab" aria-selected="false">Postgraduate</button>
          <button class="tabs__trigger" role="tab" aria-selected="false">Short Courses</button>
        </div>
        <div class="tabs__panel" role="tabpanel">
          <p class="text-body">Explore our undergraduate degree programmes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
